A) Brief description:

This collection contains 501 advertisement slogans used in the "You had me at hello" paper referenced above.


B) The slogans were collected from various online sources, including:

http://www.adslogans.co.uk/hof/
http://www.ad-mad.com/slogans
http://www.thinkslogans.com/slogans/advertising-slogans/
http://www.scribd.com/doc/48574717/advertisement-slogans

The resulting collection was manually curated.


